Package: ffread
Type: Package
Title: Extension of data.table::fread() for Efficient Large File Reading with Filtering
Version: 0.1.0
Description: This package provides an extension of the 'data.table::fread' function, allowing for efficient reading of large datasets with specific filtering capabilities. The 'ffread' function enhances 'fread' by enabling users to read only the necessary rows based on a specified key and value, optimizing the data loading process for large files.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    data.table (>= 1.12.8)
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
